  "name": "RPlog_Coronation_Pre-Game",
  "title": "Coronation Pre-Game: A Ghost on Selene",
  "summary": "On the eve of Princess Sonja's coronation, the Imperial capital world of Selene throbs with planet-wide celebration as Imperium Moffs, Caspian delegates, and the visiting Hapan court mingle in Imperator Circle. The long-vanished Sith Thane Axel Vichten, gaunt and broken after a decade of secret imprisonment aboard a black-ops prison ship, drifts hooded through the crowd until the Sith acolyte Aeron Corvus identifies and collects him at the Imperator's order. Drawn into a private audience, Axel reunites with Grand Moff Elana Tracer and Presav Crestian Tarasar before Darth Malign, the Imperator himself, welcomes the 'ghost' back, pardons all his crimes, declares him a citizen, and outlines his grand vision of a Sith Imperium that makes everyone strong. Axel, consumed by vengeance against impostors defiling the Olumi Osahn brotherhood, accepts a fast armed ship from Tracer and Crestian's offered help getting reoriented. Weary and unready for crowds, he is escorted to a hotel for solitude, having already quietly released a holonet video that will reach Selene in time.",
